content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, and more.

When sifting through business data, Salesforce CRM Analytics helps discover compelling stories within your data and create the right visuals to tell your story.

Learn to Explore Data by interactively exploring and visualizing your data using CRM Analytics tools. Use tables to get a view of the data or manipulate and extend it to expose fresh insights.

Visualize Data With Charts to understand vast amounts of business data and communicate that understanding with others. Create dynamic charts that look sharp and communicate volumes.

Clone a Lens, Save a Visualization, and Share a Visualization by posting to Chatter, getting its unique URL, downloading a screenshot, or downloading filtered data.

SEE ALSO: Converse with Your Data
title: Exploring and Visualizing Business Data in CRM Analytics
